<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Jeckie</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-11 09:39:16</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ok, I got my Mask of Deception when I was lvl 15 and it does procs then, a friend I went with was lvl 14 and his didn't work yet, you can SNEAK/HIDE by Ghouls in LGUK, so it is very easy to get to, but I suggest getting SoW so you don't walk as slow, and make sure you swimming is up pretty high, not gonna be easy to sneak/hide swimming.<BR>
<BR>
And when looting, your hide WILL break even if you see yourself or not, watch out for gargoyles, they DO see through hide, and when in Assassin room, if Assassin spawns, he does see through hide. Everything else will be fine.<BR>
<BR>
Jeckie Chan Ring of Shadows<BR>
lvl 35 Wood Elf Rogue<BR>
Veeshan</font></td></tr></table>
